_sText:
This map includes:
- a gun toss ramp
- a shot for shot area
- 6 cells
- a sniper tower
- 2 rebellion paths
- a chicken arena
- a one sided wall

There is 40 slots. 20 ct and 20 t.

Thanks to Trexx and Bob Loblaw for hammer help.
Thanks to A Campin Fool for the idea.
